Package Description
com.github.tadukoo.util.pojo
Contains MappedPojo, OrderedMappedPojo, and Table to help with general Pojos
  • Classes in com.github.tadukoo.util.pojo used by com.github.tadukoo.util.pojo
    Class Description
    AbstractMappedPojo
    Abstract Mapped Pojo is a simple implementation of the MappedPojo interface that uses a HashMap as its backing Map.
    MappedPojo
    Represents a Pojo that holds its values in a Map.
    OrderedMappedPojo
    Ordered Mapped Pojo represents a MappedPojo where the key order matters.
    Table
    Tables hold MappedPojos in them as rows.
